; Regression test for issue #846: Account directive not giving warning with --strict (BZ#846)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/846
; --strict should warn when a transaction uses an account not declared with an account directive.
; Bug was that no warning was produced; now correctly produces a warning.

account Assets:Cash
commodity $

2024/01/01 Test transaction
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --strict
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
__ERROR__
Warning: "$FILE", line 10: Unknown account 'Expenses:Food'
end test
